<%= image_tag "sign_worker.png", class: 'min-w-full' %>
<div class="grid grid-cols-7">
  <div class="bg-red-100">
    <div class="flex flex-col left-menu js-left-menu">
      <%= link_to 'About Us', workers_path, class: 'left-menu-focused', data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Practice Managers', worker_path('practice_manager'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Dentists', worker_path('dentist'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Hygienists', worker_path('hygienist'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Nurses', worker_path('nurse'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Doctors', worker_path('doctor'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
      <%= link_to 'Receptionists', worker_path('receptionist'), data: { turbo_frame: :tf_content } %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-4 p-4">
    <h2>The Sunbury Dental Team</h2>

    <div class="mt-4 content">
      <turbo-frame id="tf_content">
        <p>The Sunbury Dental Practice has a reputation for serving the local community in a warm, friendly and completely professional environment. Our team has the expertise and technology to treat both simple and advanced cases: fillings, root canal treatment, dentures, dental implants, tooth whitening and periodontal treatment for gum disease. We are renowned for our skills in restorative and cosmetic dentistry, helping our patients to look and feel better with healthy teeth and attractive smiles.</p>

        <p>We provide excellent treatment that caters to all your dental needs, at prices that you can afford. We hope that your visits are as pleasant as possible both in terms of satisfaction and convenience and we look forward to continuing to care for your dental health.</p>

        <p>All dentists, hygienists and nurses maintain their registration with the General Dental Council by attending a wide variety of lectures, courses and study groups on a regular basis.</p>
    </div>
      </turbo-frame>
  </div>
  <div class="col-span-2 hidden lg:block bg-yellow-100">
    <%= image_tag "sign_right_worker.png", class: "p-2 border border-gray-200 bg-white" %>
  </div>
</div>
